      <file change-type="modify">
        src/solutions/SpaarkeAi/src/components/compose/ComposeWorkspace.tsx
        — Added ComposeCheckoutStatus type (6 values), ComposeCheckoutLockedByInfo
        interface, 5 reducer actions (skipped/requested/acquired/conflict/failed),
        reducer branches for each, and the SPE check-out useEffect that fires
        POST /api/documents/{sprkDocumentId}/checkout via authenticatedFetch
        when status === 'loaded' and sprkDocumentId is present. Renders a
        warning MessageBar for 409 conflicts (cross-user lock; task 051 swaps
        for richer multi-tab UX) and an info MessageBar for 4xx/5xx/network
        failures (non-fatal — editor remains usable). Tier 3 discipline:
        only Tier 1 metadata logged (status, sprkDocumentId, lockedByName,
        checkedOutAt). Path B ephemeral docs (no sprkDocumentId) skip
        checkout; retry triggered automatically on Save promotion via the
        existing saveSucceeded → reducer.documentRef update flow.
